1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,500
An unfamiliar ceiling.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:15,500
This is... a hospital? I'm alive?

3
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:22,500
Shinji Ikari, all physical examination results are within normal range. You've been cleared for discharge.

4
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,500
After analyzing the combat data from Unit-01, we've discovered something intriguing.

5
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:36,500
The synchronization rate peaked at 41.3 percent. An astounding figure for the Third Child.

6
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,500
However, the data during the berserk state was unrecordable. All monitors went off the scale.

7
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:50,500
Starting today, you'll be living here. I'm Misato Katsuragi. Nice to meet you.

8
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:57,500
I'm going to live with the NERV Director of Operations?

9
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:04,500
Don't be so formal. You can't do anything on your own, can you?

10
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:12,000
Analysis of the Angel's tissue shows that 99.89 percent of its composition is identical to humans.

11
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:19,000
In other words, Angels and humans may share a common origin?

12
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:26,000
That information is classified top secret. Record it only in the MAGI system.

13
00:01:29,500 --> 00:01:33,000
Commander Ikari, the committee is requesting a report on the Third Child's aptitude.

14
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:40,000
No issue. That boy has no choice but to pilot the Eva.

15
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:47,000
Why did I get in the Eva? Was it because I wanted Father's approval?

16
00:01:50,500 --> 00:01:54,000
I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away.

17
00:01:57,500 --> 00:02:01,000
Starting tomorrow, you'll report to NERV headquarters. You are now officially an Eva pilot.

18
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:08,000
Ikari, you will undergo a pilot aptitude evaluation and basic training.

19
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:15,000
Adjusting LCL concentration inside the entry plug. Beginning neural connection test.

20
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:22,000
Synchronization rate, stable. No issues. Shinji Ikari, certified as Eva Unit-01's designated pilot.
